title: Email Delivery Pipeline

participant Sender MUA as Sender
participant Sending MTA as SMTA
participant DNS as DNS
participant Receiving MTA as RMTA
participant SpamAssassin as Spam
participant Mailbox as MB
participant Recipient MUA as Recip

Sender->>SMTA: SMTP: MAIL FROM, RCPT TO, DATA
SMTA->>SMTA: DKIM sign message
SMTA->>DNS: MX lookup for recipient.com
DNS-->>SMTA: mx1.recipient.com (priority 10)
SMTA->>RMTA: SMTP STARTTLS + deliver message
note over RMTA: Check SPF record
RMTA->>DNS: TXT lookup _spf.sender.com
DNS-->>RMTA: v=spf1 include:mail.sender.com
note right of RMTA: SPF: PASS
note over RMTA: Verify DKIM signature
RMTA->>DNS: TXT lookup selector._domainkey.sender.com
DNS-->>RMTA: DKIM public key
note right of RMTA: DKIM: PASS
RMTA->>Spam: Score message
Spam-->>RMTA: Score: 1.2 (ham)
note right of RMTA: Below spam threshold (5.0)
RMTA->>MB: Deliver to INBOX
MB-->>RMTA: Stored
RMTA-->>SMTA: 250 OK
Recip->>MB: IMAP FETCH
MB-->>Recip: New message from Sender
